<topic id="relational-dbexplorer-table-actions">
  <title>Actions Available at Table Level in Data Source Explorer View</title>
  <!--Proofed-->
  <body>
    <p>The contextual menu of a <uicontrol>
        <image href="../img/bt_db_table.png"/> Table </uicontrol> node in the tree from the
        <uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol> view contains the following actions:</p>
    <dl>
      <dlentry>
        <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Refresh16.png" id="image_x1p_pfw_sr"
          />Refresh</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Performs a refresh for the sub-tree of the selected node.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry>
        <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/bt_view_schema.png" placement="inline"
          />Edit</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Opens the selected table in the <uicontrol>Table Explorer</uicontrol> view.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry>
        <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/bt_export_to_xml.png" placement="inline"/>Export to
            XML</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Opens the <uicontrol>Export Criteria</uicontrol> dialog <ph
            product="editor editorEclipse developer developerEclipse">(a thorough description of
            this dialog can be found in the <xref
              href="../tasks/import-db-table-content-to-xml.dita">Import from Database</xref>
            chapter)</ph> . </dd>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>
  </body>
</topic>